From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarun <noreply@sarun>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 17:47:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] find: probe type arguments through execution parser

Add an effect-free, Find-owned argument probe for starting paths and the -type/-xtype slice. Exact and assist inputs replay parse_args, build_matcher_tree, and type_creator; unsupported expression arms are rejected before parse-time effects.

